dataLineage.statement:
Layer was downloaded as a shapefile by ITOS from HDX. It was then analyzed by ITOS for errors. Those errors were corrected and then the layer was sent back to UNOCHA as a feature class within a file geodatabase.
The following errors were found and fixed by ITOS: 1. District names converted from ALL CAPS to Proper Case. 2. Two Admin3 units with two polygons were merged into 1 multipart feature: Binayi Tribeni (NP0447404) and Bansgadhi (NP0558306) 3. Appended Admin1 p-codes with 2-letter ISO code "NL" 4. Created and populated Admin0 name and p-code fields.
The following was found but is not addressed in this version: 1. 4 Admin3 names are duplicated within the same Admin2: Dhorpatan, Lumbini Sanskritik, Shivapuri, Shuklaphanta. They have unique AltNames and p-codes
